*Trag* je potražio izgubljenog psa. (The trace was searched for the lost dog.)

*Tragovi* su se vidjeli po snegu. (Traces were seen in the snow.)

Njegov *trag* je bio prisutan u svakoj sobi. (His trace was present in every room.)

Njegova *traga* se nikad nije pronalažila. (His trace was never found.)

*Tragovima* koji je ostavio, oni su uspeli da pronađu njegovo skriveno mesto. (By the traces he left, they were able to find his hidden place.)